NAZ AT A GLANCE: Athletic skillset ... Multi-dimensional player ... Strong basketball pedigree.

FRESHMAN (2015-16): Appeared in one game, playing four minutes.

HIGH SCHOOL: Honorable Mention All-County selection by the Oakland Press at Detroit Country Day ... As a senior, averaged 11.4 ppg, 5.7 reb, 1.5 steals ... Scored 28 points in a win over Holly (Dec. 10) ... Scored in double figures in 11 games ... Scored over 20 points in two games ... Yellow Jackets won Michigan Class B state championship during his sophomore year in 2013 ... Also ran track.

PERSONAL: Son of Rasheed and Fatima Wallace ... Has two older brothers, Malik and Ishmiel, and a younger sister, Rashiyah ... Psychology major.
